@BlinkRush_HostAddress = http://localhost:5281

### Create Speed Run record
POST {{BlinkRush_HostAddress}}/api/records
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mode": "speedRun",
  "value": 12.345,
  "deviceId": "device-abc-123",
  "name": "PlayerOne",
  "occurredAt": null
}

### Create Endurance record
POST {{BlinkRush_HostAddress}}/api/records
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mode": "endurance",
  "value": 42,
  "deviceId": "device-abc-123",
  "name": null
}

### Leaderboard Speed Run (best times first)
GET {{BlinkRush_HostAddress}}/api/leaderboard?mode=speedRun&take=20
Accept: application/json

### Leaderboard Endurance (most blinks first)
GET {{BlinkRush_HostAddress}}/api/leaderboard?mode=endurance&take=20
Accept: application/json

### User leaderboard Speed Run (best time per device)
GET {{BlinkRush_HostAddress}}/api/users/leaderboard?mode=speedRun&take=20
Accept: application/json

### User leaderboard Endurance (best blinks per device)
GET {{BlinkRush_HostAddress}}/api/users/leaderboard?mode=endurance&take=20
Accept: application/json

###
